room_title: Escape room "Wizard Room" by Escape Room Breckenridge in Breckenridge
room_address: 233 South Ridge Street, Suite C, Breckenridge, CO 80424
room_description: You and your group are students of the Breckenridge Wizard School. School is not in session, but you just received an alert that there is a large troll ransacking the town of Breck. You know that trolls love eating magical owls so you and your crew are breaking into the school to save the school pet owl. Can you break into the school, find your beloved owl and escape in time?
